room_title: Escape room "The Zombie Kitchen" by TeamEscape 262 in Milwaukee
review: A lot of fun. There were 5 of us in the zombie kitchen and it took all five of us to escape. Very well put together!!

room_title: Escape room "The Zombie Kitchen" by TeamEscape 262 in Milwaukee
review: We spent a fun afternoon attempting to escape Zombie Kitchen. We were disappointed that we were unable to make it out in time.. just a few more minutes and we prob would have lol. We did have a lot of fun though. It was harder than I expected it to be and a little creepy but with a name like Zombie Kitchen you know up front that creepy is the theme. My favorite part was afterwards they had great photo props. It is a great team bonding opportunity. We laughed so much!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Zombie Kitchen" by TeamEscape 262 in Milwaukee
review: Our family did the Zombie Kitchen and had so much fun. Great time spent with the family. We will definitely come back to do more rooms!
